/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is flanked by lush greenery, with trees and grass adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many urban areas. In the distance, a bridge stretches across the scene, connecting different parts of the city. The sky above is a clear blue, dotted with white clouds, adding a serene backdrop to the busy street below.
